# ServiceNow Developer Portal Authentication
# Get these values from developer.servicenow.com:
# 1. Login to developer.servicenow.com
# 2. Open browser DevTools (F12) and go to Network tab
# 3. Navigate to any API documentation page (e.g., https://developer.servicenow.com/app.do#!/api_doc?v=newyork&type=server&id=no-namespace)
# 4. Find a request to 'devportal.do' 
# 5. Copy the Cookie header value (entire string)
# 6. Copy the X-UserToken header value

# Example format (these are not real values):
# COOKIE=BIGipServerpool_prod=123456789.12345.0000; JSESSIONID=ABCD1234; glide_user_route=glide.1234abcd; ...
# USER_TOKEN=1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef

COOKIE=your_cookie_value_here
USER_TOKEN=your_user_token_value_here